import React from 'react'
import Input from './Input'
import Textarea from './Textarea'


const FormikControl = (props) => {
  const {control, ...rest}=props
  switch (control) {
    case 'input': 
        return <Input {...rest}/>
    case 'textarea':  
        return <Textarea {...rest}/>
    case 'select':  
    case 'radio':  
    case 'checkbox':  
    case 'data': 
    default: return null
  }
}

export default FormikControl
